records.name: Kandolhu Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Kandolhu, Kandolhu Maldives is on a private beach. Folhudhoo Harbor and Ukulhas Harbor are local landmarks, and some of the area's activities can be experienced at Himendhoo Thila and Feridhoo Harbor. Looking to get your feet wet? Scuba diving, snorkeling and windsurfing adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Even in the Maldives an island so perfectly formed as Kandolhu is rare The island is lush with wide sandy beaches surrounding the emerald green and is home to one of the most colorful and lively house reef in the MaldivesEven in the Maldives an island so perfectly formed as Kandolhu is rare The island is lush with wide sandy beaches surrounding the emerald green and is home to one of the most colorful and lively house reef in the Maldives
